<div id="comment_status_64587943" class="commentstatus"></div>
<div id="comment_64587943" class="cw">
	<div id="comment_top_64587943" class="commentTop newcomment">
		<div class="title">
			<h4><a id="comment_link_64587943" name="comment_link_64587943" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23371833&amp;cid=64587943" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64587943)" >Control group showed the same signal</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64587943" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64587943); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>4</a>, Interesting)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~sinij">sinij</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~sinij">( 911942 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64587943">		
		on Saturday June 29, 2024 @01:35PM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23371833&amp;cid=64587943">#64587943</a>)
		<small> </small>
</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64587943">According to the article, the control group showed similar improvements. Therefore, it is not due to UBI.</div>
	</div>

